GHS office_panic

==============
Revamped version of the original
[Added] More Props
[Added] Another Secret Area
[Change] Time of day from morning to night
[Fixed] Falling off Map problems
================
There is alot of areas to explore, if this is your first time seeing this map I will briefly go over whats included inside:
Theres 3 Floors, 1st,2nd,and rooftop, lots of secret rooms and special powers such as Zombie Advantages: Can turn off the lights for the 1st floor...On the 2nd floor zombies can press a button allowing shutters to drop for couple of seconds trapping the humans.

-WaterPyro
-GHS
